# ⚙️ Machine Learning Techniques Used

## 🔹 Undersampling

Reduces the number of normal transactions to balance the dataset.

## 🔹 SMOTE (Synthetic Minority Oversampling Technique)

Generates synthetic fraud samples to improve model performance.

## 🔹 Isolation Forest

An anomaly detection algorithm used to identify fraudulent transactions.

